text: Yemi Osinbajo It is time for Nigeria to start doing business - Pulse Nigeria Pulse Nigeria “As part of our work on the Ease of Doing Business , on making the environment friendly, not just for local businesses but also for those who want to come and do business in Nigeria , the airport obviously is one of the major places where we need to …
